	<name>Advanced Metronome</name>
	<summary>Advanced Metronome is a small application in which you can set multiple measures.</summary>
	<translation type="gettext">advancedmetronome</translation>
	
	<description>
		<p>
			Advanced Metronome is created for musicians who want to practice songs which have multiple
			speeds and/or time-durations. &lsquo;Cause regular metronomes only allow one constant tempo Advanced Metronome
			steps in to solve this problem.
		</p>

		<p>
			Advanced Metronome also gives you the ability to save and share your songs with others so this application will
			suit many bands in their song-writing process.
		</p>
	</description>
	
